strings: <voice_0x01001635><se_low>Meaning<:> Why?!
<voice_0x01001636><se_low>Develop your competencies!

<voice_0x0100163A>Rapthorn opens a portal between the world of light and the world of darkness. I did it
<voice_0x0100163B>But countless people from the dark race chased me and attacked me!
<voice_0x0100163C>His evil disciples have wiped out nearly all life on Earth.
<voice_0x0100163D>Lapthorne's body was there already. Now this problem has crossed the upper limit.
<voice_0x0100163E>Our only solution is to defeat him in battle <hero>.
<voice_0x0100163F>It's so powerful it's the only way to save the planet.
<voice_0x01001640>But the odds of winning are slim... You are our only hope.
<voice_0x01001641>You have the <hero> blood of the chosen one... The <hero> light shines on you.
<voice_0x01001642>This time, however, Larsen is protected by a very powerful shield.
<voice_0x01001643>Therefore it is invulnerable and must be removed first.
<voice_0x01001644>put your hands up
<voice_0x01001645>A whistle sounded.
<voice_0x01001646>Lappthorne's shield is indestructible. Need help?
<voice_0x01001647>With the help of the Seven Sages... the warriors had already sealed Raphson.
<voice_0x01001648>I feel the strength of your will. They have returned to help us defeat the Dark Lord.
<voice_0x01001649>It is in the shape of seven magic pearls. Each of them has the power of a saint.
<voice_0x0100164A>Use the whistle to find out. They are distributed throughout the world. But you have to collect them.
<voice_0x0100164B>When you play the flute and approach the ball, there is a resonance or reaction.
<voice_0x0100164C>Where once there were seven sages, now there are seven states.
<voice_0x0100164D>You must collect all seven before returning to me.
<voice_0x0100164E>I want to find something to do, so I must go. But I will be back
<voice_0x0100164F>Time is up <hero>. Long story short!
